Package: apache
Architecture: any
Depends: libc6, libdb4.2, libgdbmg1, libssl0.9.8, openssl
Description: Apache 2.0
 Custom built statically compiled version of Apache 2.0 which installs into
 /usr/local/apache.  Includes mod_ssl support with auto-generation of
 self-signed certs if certs are not already present.  Also includes functional
 default configurations for both http and https.  Logs to /var/log/apache/*
